            "type": "text",
            "text": "In production systems, OCR costs can spiral unexpectedly when processing thousands of documents daily. Nanonets OCR S addresses this by offering a balanced model that prioritizes accuracy without exorbitant pricing, but teams must dissect its cost structure to avoid budget overruns. This post breaks down the Nanonets OCR S cost model, providing concrete data and strategies to manage expenses effectively."
