      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We'll explore the pricing tiers, performance characteristics, and integration steps that directly impact your bottom line. By the end, you'll have a clear framework to estimate costs, optimize usage, and compare alternatives for your specific workload."
