            "text": "In real-world tests, the model achieves 95-98% accuracy on printed text, reducing the need for manual corrections that add hidden labor costs. For handwritten or low-quality images, accuracy may drop to 85-90%, potentially increasing post-processing expenses. Monitor these metrics using the API's response headers, which include processing time and confidence scores, to fine-tune your cost-performance ratio."
